title: American imports of corn 2001 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Imports in million bushels, containing a total of 19 data points.
Overall Imports in million bushels has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2011 and 2012.
The highest Imports in million bushels, of value 160.0 was reached at Year 2012
Minimum Imports in million bushels about 8.0 was reached at Year 2009
